eu.profinit.manta.dataflow.repository.model.domain

Class MapsTo

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.profinit.manta.dataflow.repository.model.domain.AbstractEdge<Node>
      • eu.profinit.manta.dataflow.repository.model.domain.MapsTo

  • public class MapsTo
extends AbstractEdge<Node>
    A maps-to edge. Maps-to edge represents relationship between nodes from different layers. It specifies that the source node from layer X is mapped to the target node from layer Y. For maps-to edges applies that this type of edge can be present only on the lowest level of the hierarchy of Nodes in both layers.
